@PatrickGuo initializeTensorflow() is a native method; can you tell if Bazel is building the native libs? Try unzip -v bazel-bin/tensorflow/examples/android/tensorflow_demo.apk | grep libtensorflow_demo.so and you should see output like:
5163140 Defl:N 1753712 66% 1980-01-01 00:00 7b8de845 lib/armeabi-v7a/libtensorflow_demo.so

Also can you build with -s --verbose_failures and attach the build log please?

@pkpp1233 Are you seeing the preview size error or the no implementation error?
